# === Large data artifacts ===
# Raw scrape CSV stays out of git (regeneratable, large, noisy diffs).
# find-school.db IS tracked so the mobile app can build straight from clone.
# If it crosses ~50 MB, switch to Git LFS or a GitHub Release asset.
scraper/schools_raw.csv
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.db-journal

